---
// SkillsSection - technical skills overview
---

<div class="p-6 ring-1 ring-zinc-200/70 dark:ring-zinc-700/40">
  <h2
    class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold font-heading text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100"
  >
    <svg
      stroke-width="1.5"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="flex-none w-6 h-6 fill-zinc-100/10 stroke-zinc-500"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        d="M9.315 7.584C12.195 3.883 16.695 1.5 21.75 1.5a.75.75 0 01.75.75c0 5.056-2.383 9.555-6.084 12.436A6.75 6.75 0 019.75 22.5a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75v-4.131A15.838 15.838 0 016.382 15H2.25a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75 6.75 6.75 0 017.815-6.666zM15 6.75a2.25 2.25 0 100 4.5 2.25 2.25 0 000-4.5z"
        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
      <path
        d="M5.26 17.242a.75.75 0 10-.897-1.203 5.243 5.243 0 00-2.05 5.022.75.75 0 00.625.627 5.243 5.243 0 005.022-2.051.75.75 0 10-1.202-.897 3.744 3.744 0 01-3.008 1.51c0-1.23.592-2.323 1.51-3.008z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
    <span class="ml-3">Compétences Techniques</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
    Au fil du temps, j'ai acquis des compétences dans divers domaines de la
    programmation. Voici quelques technologies que j'utilise régulièrement.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
    {
      [
        "Vue.js",
        "ReactJS",
        "Next.js",
        "Tanstack",
        "Zustand",
        "Laravel",
        "Livewire",
        "Alpine.js",
        "Tailwind CSS",
        "Jest",
      ].map((skill) => (
        <span class="inline-flex items-center bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-600 ring-1 ring-inset ring-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:ring-zinc-700">
          {skill}
        </span>
      ))
    }
  </div>
</div>
